# Base URL of the Ginja platform API.
# Responses are snake_case and wrapped in a { status, success, result, error_details } envelope.
#
# Leave this UNSET for normal local dev: the app defaults to the relative "/api/v1"
# path, which the Vite dev proxy (vite.config.ts) forwards to the Azure host so the
# browser stays same-origin and never hits CORS. Production builds default to the
# absolute Azure URL below.
#
# Set it only to override (e.g. point dev at a locally-run backend):
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8082/api/v1
#
# Deployed API host (used by prod builds; also the proxy target in vite.config.ts):
# https://dev-api.ginja.ai/internal-platform/api/v1
